  "returns": "Array of INotes",
  "remarks": "This method automatically inserts BOM balloons for bill of materials items in selected drawing views. If a drawing sheet is selected, BOM balloons are automatically inserted for all of the drawing views on that drawing sheet.\nTo automatically insert BOM balloons:\nSelect one or more views or sheets for which to automatically create BOM balloons.\nCall\nIDrawingDoc::CreateAutoBalloonOptions\nto create an\nIAutoBalloonOptions\nobject.\nSet the properties on the IAutoBalloonOptions object.\nCall this method using the IAutoBalloonOptions object in the BalloonOptions argument.",
